	(text_box "The maximum power that can be consumed by the system is 13W, and the maximum power that could be consumed by periperhals (M.2 & USB-A ports) is 20.4W. Not all sources are able to provide this power so the perhiperal power must be limited:\n\n- 5V USB (3A capable): 2W for peripherals\n- 5V USB (5A capable): 12W for peripherals\n- 12V VIN: 5W for peripherals\n- 24V VIN: 20W for peripherals\n\nNote that the USB-A ports cannot consume more than 10W combined."
